  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0851ea360a87bf44bac72430d6f27a40, type: 3}
  description: "\u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh n\u1EB1m \u1EDF khu
    v\u1EF1c T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn, n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi nh\u1EEFng cao nguy\xEAn
    r\u1ED9ng l\u1EDBn v\xE0 thi\xEAn nhi\xEAn h\xF9ng v\u0129. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a
    t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Bu\xF4n Ma Thu\u1ED9t, \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    xem l\xE0 \u201Cth\u1EE7 ph\u1EE7 c\xE0 ph\xEA\u201D c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam.
    \u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk c\xF2n h\u1EA5p d\u1EABn du kh\xE1ch v\u1EDBi c\xE1c \u0111\u1ECBa
    danh n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng nh\u01B0 H\u1ED3 L\u1EAFk v\xE0 Th\xE1c Dray Nur. Ngo\xE0i
    ra, n\u01A1i \u0111\xE2y c\xF2n c\xF3 n\u1EC1n v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c
    s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c nh\u01B0 \xCA \u0110\xEA, M\u2019n\xF4ng
    v\u1EDBi nh\u1EEFng l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng, nh\xE0 d\xE0i v\xE0
    kh\xF4ng gian v\u0103n h\xF3a c\u1ED3ng chi\xEAng \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng c\u1EE7a
    v\xF9ng T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn."
  desSatNhap: "Theo quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c t\u1EA1i Ngh\u1ECB
    quy\u1EBFt s\u1ED1 202/2025/QH15, t\u1EC9nh \u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk s\u1EBD th\u1EF1c
    hi\u1EC7n t\xE1i c\u1EA5u tr\xFAc kh\xF4ng gian h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u1EDF quy m\xF4
    l\u1EDBn ch\u01B0a t\u1EEBng c\xF3. C\u1EE5 th\u1EC3, Qu\u1ED1c h\u1ED9i quy\u1EBFt
    \u0111\u1ECBnh s\xE1p nh\u1EADp to\xE0n b\u1ED9 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn
    v\xE0 quy m\xF4 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh Ph\xFA Y\xEAn v\xE0o t\u1EC9nh
    \u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk, h\xECnh th\xE0nh n\xEAn m\u1ED9t \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB
    h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh m\u1EDBi v\u1EABn gi\u1EEF t\xEAn g\u1ECDi l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh \u0110\u1EAFk
    L\u1EAFk.\r\n\r\nS\u1EF1 s\xE1p nh\u1EADp n\xE0y ki\u1EBFn t\u1EA1o n\xEAn m\u1ED9t
    v\u1ECB th\u1EBF \u0111\u1ECBa ch\xEDnh tr\u1ECB \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t cho
    \u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk m\u1EDBi, n\u1ED1i li\u1EC1n m\u1EA1ch m\xE1u giao th\xF4ng
    v\xE0 kinh t\u1EBF t\u1EEB \u0111\u1EA1i ng\xE0n T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn xu\u1ED1ng
    duy\xEAn h\u1EA3i Nam Trung B\u1ED9."
